{"tid":2366344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方國安處拘捕多人包括黃國桐律師，料今日被扣查暫不安排保釋","createTime":"2021-01-14T12:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T03:49:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b66f1db30e5bd0dcb36b859a144a5731a0a2a43f","tid":2366344,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570390-20210114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570390-20210114.htm&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=5edcc985\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570390-20210114.htm&h=c9298345\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570390-20210114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處國安處今早採取行動，據了解，在多區拘捕11名涉嫌「協助罪犯」的人士，包括8男3女，年齡介乎18至72歲。據悉是涉及12港人案件，預料被捕人士今日會被扣留調查，暫時不會安排保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士中，包括九龍城區議員黃國桐、學聯前副秘書長何潔泓的母親等。警方中午前帶黃國桐返回位於福佬村道的議員辦事處搜查，離開時黃國桐高叫堅持民主、法治、人權，不要放棄的口號。"},{"pid":"7a65678b4b3a069b5a0fd0905ccc1ecdf7b83199","tid":2366344,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"釋放義士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9e91152bb3bf14a6204c4c2d1f0c7c2b1ea241","tid":2366344,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3572d21c3cab244eeeb92e3969ab366468b4be0a","tid":2366344,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">涉嫌「協助罪犯」的人士</span><br />\n所有律師拉曬佢啦你老味"},{"pid":"cac3fac62b4a8759375154a5e00c17574c2d71ae","tid":2366344,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit